---
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section id="about" class="relative py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <SectionHeader
      eyebrow="About"
      title="Operator instincts. Builder reps."
    />
    <div class="reveal mx-auto mt-14 grid max-w-4xl gap-8 text-lg text-mist-300 md:grid-cols-2">
      <p>
        I have spent ten years scaling identity, trust, and ML systems at Airbnb and Twitter. Today I lead 19 engineers across Identity Platform, Defense, and Business Verification. Our systems protect millions of users every day and delivered $23.9M in annualized impact last year.
      </p>
      <p>
        In parallel I built and shipped <a href="https://loadout.hellomilo.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-400/40 underline-offset-4 transition hover:text-accent-300 hover:decoration-accent-300" data-track="cta_loadout_about">Loadout</a>, a five-layer Claude Code operating system with an 8-chapter guide and starter pack. Solo, end-to-end, in under 5 days. Now looking for the right zero-to-one team where operator discipline and founder velocity matter equally.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
